snippet.title: Terror Squid: Developer Gameplay Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Creative director Syver Lauritzsen walks you through about four minutes of gameplay from his team's upcoming arcade survival game, Terror Squid. Its release date is scheduled for later this year on all platforms.
